        ggraph, fgsea, limma, ComplexHeatmap, geneset,
        genekitr2, qs, jsonlite, parallel,
        ggnewscale, ggrepel, scales, circlize, methods, grid
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), knitr, rmarkdown
